20:06.553 --> 20:08.032
The Sandman
wants to hurt us,

20:08.076 --> 20:09.730
which means
if we don't stop this soon,

20:09.773 --> 20:12.515
every adult in town,
whatever their age,

20:12.559 --> 20:14.256
