20:35.886 --> 20:37.932
hurt somebody.

20:38.933 --> 20:41.283
What about yours?Uh...

20:41.327 --> 20:44.286
I just, uh...

20:44.330 --> 20:46.375
I think my subconscious
was trying to tell me

20:46.419 --> 20:49.422
