that I haven't followed.

20:50.597 --> 20:52.555
About Trott.

20:52.599 --> 20:54.253
BESS:
Okay, I feel
like I saw something

20:54.296 --> 20:57.125
in the Women in White's journal
a-about a sleep charm.

