She only does something
if it's gonna benefit her.

21:04.175 --> 21:06.134
Okay. So,
what if it benefits us, too?

21:06.177 --> 21:07.266
Yeah, for all we know,
Temperance

21:07.309 --> 21:08.484
could be
behind what's happening.

21:08.528 --> 21:10.443
Uh, well,
she's not that bad of a person.

21:10.486 --> 21:12.314
Oh, please. You
don't even know her.BESS: Yes,

21:12.358 --> 21:14.795
I do, actually.NANCY:Okay.

21:14.838 --> 21:17.493
I've been visiting Temperance
a little bit.

21:17.537 --> 21:19.452
GEORGE:
You what?

21:19.495 --> 21:21.454
Over the past few days.

21:21.497 --> 21:23.543
NANCY:
Why?

21:23.586 --> 21:26.067
She's not your friend, Bess.
Don't let her fool you.BESS: At least

21:26.110 --> 21:27.329
Temperance takes me seriously

