21:30.027 --> 21:32.769
She's even helping me become
a Woman in White.

21:32.813 --> 21:34.075
Those don't exist anymore.

21:34.118 --> 21:35.816
Yeah, Bess, that's
like me saying

21:35.859 --> 21:37.165
I want to become a Pilgrim.

21:37.208 --> 21:38.558
Like...[others laugh]

21:38.601 --> 21:40.516
You know what? Forget it.

21:40.560 --> 21:42.823
You know what?
You're too busy making the calls

21:42.866 --> 21:44.607
