23:20.747 --> 23:22.531
She helped me find
the sleep charm that...

23:22.575 --> 23:25.229
Oh, dear. Oh, no. Oh, no.

23:25.273 --> 23:27.884
Hey, Nancy?
Nancy, can you hear me?

23:27.928 --> 23:29.364
You have to wake up!

23:30.931 --> 23:33.150
Oh, yes.

23:33.194 --> 23:34.761
I am so sorry.

23:34.804 --> 23:36.589
I just really need to know
what you guys were up to

23:36.632 --> 23:38.678
before the handcuffs
and the sleeping.

23:39.722 --> 23:42.333
[phone unlocks]And I won't
go through your texts.

23:42.377 --> 23:43.987
Unless...

23:44.031 --> 23:46.163
No, no, I promise. I promise.

23:46.207 --> 23:47.904
Okay.

23:47.948 --> 23:50.603
Coastal tribes believed
the entity was originally

23:50.646 --> 23:53.388
created from particles of sand
at Piper Beach.

23:53.432 --> 23:55.695
Hence the name, I suppose.

23:57.261 --> 24:00.264
