24:17.543 --> 24:19.545
[grunting]

24:24.332 --> 24:27.727
Oh, no. Oh, no.

24:28.902 --> 24:30.773
Oh, my God.
[gasps]

24:30.817 --> 24:32.601
The Sandman is getting stronger.

24:32.645 --> 24:35.430
Ace, Ace,
you need to wake up. Ace.

24:36.475 --> 24:38.433
Gosh, Ace, please.

24:42.437 --> 24:45.658
Come on, Ryan.
Pick up the phone.

24:45.701 --> 24:47.181
Oh, gosh.

24:49.531 --> 24:51.968
CARTER:
George Li-Yun Fan

24:52.012 --> 24:54.449
also leaves behind
her loving father,

24:54.493 --> 24:57.060
Edwin George Chen.

24:57.104 --> 24:58.975
