25:02.065 --> 25:04.024
But now it's too late.

25:04.067 --> 25:06.069
Wait! Wait!

25:06.113 --> 25:07.418
What are you doing?!

25:07.462 --> 25:09.377
Stop! Stop, I'm not dead!

25:09.420 --> 25:11.727
