29:47.437 --> 29:49.396
Come on, Bess.

29:49.439 --> 29:51.398
Come on.

29:53.966 --> 29:55.706
Follow me.

30:13.637 --> 30:15.639
Now we lure it.

30:21.036 --> 30:22.908
Not this time.

30:22.951 --> 30:25.388
